div.div: Created new tag v1.0.0-stable in hesphoros/LightLogWriteLib

Add LightLogWriteImpl project with lock-free logging implementation
- Created Visual Studio solution and project files for LightLogWriteImpl. - Implemented LockFreeLogWriteImpl class for efficient, thread-safe logging. - Added convert_tools for string encoding conversions (UTF-8, UCS-4, UTF-16). - Developed performance measurement utility to compare logging implementations. - Included necessary headers and defined logging structures and enums. - Established a lock-free queue to handle log messages without blocking. - Implemented file handling and logging mechanisms with multi-threading support.
